# Shared defaults load from `packages/expo-env-loader/base.env`.
# App-specific overrides belong in `.env.local` (gitignored).
# Optional personal overrides belong in `.env` (gitignored).
# See `apps/ENVIRONMENT.example.md` for the full load chain.
#
# Required app-specific key in `.env.local`:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_EAS_PROJECT_ID=<uuid>
#
# Optional app-specific keys (if not already provided by EAS profile env):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_IOS_CLIENT_ID=<client-id>
# EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID=<client-id>
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=<dsn>
